Key chaaracteristics of Adult Learners
(Adult learners desire that learning should be...)
-Relevant
-Task/Result/Goal Oriented
-Participatory
-Friendly (Positive Feedback)
-Varied (case study, role play, deonstratiom)
-Built on Past Experiences


